data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION, brings you here. A rare to fine opportunity in Grassy Key. This home sits on a 20,000 sqft, .46 acre lot with lots of shaded trees, beautiful 2/1 original 1160sqft conch bungalow. Once back in the days this building housed the famous 'Hidey Hole' Bar & Grill. It was converted and renovated into a comfortable home with high ceilings in the living and dining area, a jacuzzi tub, impact windows, metal roof, lots of storage freshly painted. Plenty of room for expansion, such as a pool, tiki, accessory structure and more! Conveniently nearby, shopping, restaurants, boat ramps fishing, snorkeling diving and more. Become the owner of a historical landmark of the Florida Keys! This home has a transient license and can be rented weekly, monthly, or yearly. Investment opportunity waits for you!
